item.title: About us
item.description: I am glad that you have found us! 😃 Here I would like to let you participate in our journey 🛤️ and to report on interesting topics in everyday dog life 🐶. You will also read more about traveling with a dog and why I started a dog trainer education 🐕. It remains exciting! Have fun on this blog! Wiebke & Pepper
